    <h1>Data Management Platform (DMP)</h1>
    <p class="description">Software that collects, organizes, and activates audience data across sources into targetable ad segments. The <strong>enterprise adtech backbone</strong> for programmatic buying — increasingly complemented by CDPs.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
