            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Enterprise DMPs range from $50,000 to $500,000+ per year depending on data volume, connected platforms, and features. There is no meaningful DMP tier under $50,000/year — small brands are better served by ad-platform native audience tools.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">What are the main use cases for a DMP?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
